title: District DMV Locations to Close for Columbus Day (District of Columbia Department of Motor Vehicles) ...
text: ( Source : District of Columbia Department of Motor Vehicles ) (WASHINGTON, DC) - In observance of Columbus Day , all District of Columbia Department of Motor Vehicles (DC DMV ) locations will be closed on Saturday, October 10 and Monday,
